name: phosphor
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "phosphor" %}
{% set version = "0.7.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "375ad74a0e555192bf21f1c412a0a499f0943eeb9048b55054397434973586cd" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://registry.npmjs.org/{{ name }}/-/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tgz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  script: npm install -g .
  skip: True  # [osx]

requirements:
  build:
    - nodejs
  
test:
  commands:
    - npm list -g phosphor
  requires:
    - nodejs
   

about:
  home: https://github.com/phosphorjs/phosphor
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'The PhosphorJS Library'
  description: |
    The PhosphorJS Library  
  doc_url: http://phosphorjs.github.io/docs.html
  dev_url: https://github.com/phosphorjs/phosphor

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cshaley
    - sannykr
